name: Different Dimension
description:
Controls: WASD or Arrow Keys to move, Space to jump, E to pickup objects. You got trapped in a different dimension where you can jump high, which is pretty cool. Oh. And you're also surrounded by lava. You need to find the two pieces of the broken portal that trapped you here in order to get back to your world. However, these two pieces are in the worst places they could possibly be. You need to use your skills to get the two pieces of the portal and return back to your world. Good luck! (You're DEFINITELY gonna fail)

Code/Design - Aura

Music - Arwen
